		JEAN'S FAMOUS TOMATO TEA		</span></strong><br />
		<FONT color=#0033ff size=5><BR>122</FONT> <STRONG>YEA</STRONG></P>
<P>Jean writes, "After drinking this recipe, your sinus congestion will disappear REAL fast. All these ingredients not only work on the immediate symptoms, but add plenty of vitamin C to fight a cold, and garlic to fight infection.</P>
<P>Recipe: <BR>Add 1 cup tomato juice, <BR>1 tsp chopped fresh garlic, <BR>1/2 tsp of hot sauce, <BR>1 tsp lemon juice, <BR>and a pinch or two of celery salt for flavor. </P>
<P>Heat ingredients and drink hot."</P>
